---
Show the calendar invite attached to one message

Usage: mxr invite show [OPTIONS] <MESSAGE_ID>

Arguments:
  <MESSAGE_ID>

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --format <FORMAT>    [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help               Print help
